"ngram\": \"four days\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We first stopped at Poznan in Poland, where Nabab rested for 10 hours.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 829, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pozna\\u0144\", \"score\": 0.9994899491136252, \"rank\": 0.0004302468136290841, \"text\": \"Poznan\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pozna\\u0144\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pozna\\u0144\"}, {\"begin\": 839, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.9994529787133674, \"rank\": 0.00048384733924244325, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}, {\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nabab\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nabab\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nabab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nabab\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10 hours\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then we went to another stable in Aachen.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"score\": 0.9999999686133383, \"rank\": 2.2950212739395073e-08, \"text\": \"Aachen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was then meant to stay in Jardy, but I had not booked the box in time and they did not have a spare one, so we stayed in Aachen for one more day.\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1046, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"score\": 0.9999999686133383, \"rank\": 2.2950212739395073e-08, \"text\": \"Aachen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jardy\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"the box\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"a spare one\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"one more day\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We then left at midnight, drove through the night, and arrived in Versailles at 6am.\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1137, \"end\": 1147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"score\": 0.9999995272556796, \"rank\": 4.727446941341942e-07, \"text\": \"Versailles\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"midnight\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The first day I was thinking, 'Oh, he must be so tired, I will give him four days' rest,\\\" explains Justina, who attended the opening ceremony as one of Lithuania'sflag-bearers.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"score\": 0.9330207840329765, \"rank\": 0.07178529385722207, \"text\": \"Justina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\"}, {\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\", \"score\": 0.9888438051117389, \"rank\": 0.01015455586439094, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four days' rest\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But when I was lungeing him he was going round and round, snorting like a dragon.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dragon\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next day he was jumping all over me so I said, 'OK, you feel quite good, I will ride you' - and he was a bit like a dragon.\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dragon\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I rode him all week without spurs and in a snaffle bridle.\\\"\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1609, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"spurs\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"a snaffle bridle\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Justina has built up a reputation on social media for having a lot of fun with her precious horse, whom she nicknames Kebab.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"score\": 0.9330207840329765, \"rank\": 0.07178529385722207, \"text\": \"Justina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\"}, {\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kebab\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kebab\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kebab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kebab\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a reputation\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"her precious horse\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From one of her final training sessions before the Olympics, she posted a video of her doing pirouettes bareback in a headcollar.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her final training sessions\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1797}, {\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"pirouettes\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1841}, {\"ngram\": \"a headcollar\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was supposed to be lungeing him, but afterwards I thought maybe I'd just get on and walk, then I started to trot a little bit - and then I thought maybe we can do some movements and do a video,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 2076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"some movements\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a showgirl,\\\" she adds.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a showgirl\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But that does not matter, I still get nervous.\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just happy I managed to hold it together compared with all the riders with so much more experience than me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the riders\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2229}, {\"ngram\": \"so much more experience\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Justina scored a creditable 69.20%, which puts her mid-division of the 30 riders to compete on day one of the grand prix qualifier.\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2270, \"end\": 2277, \"title